                    <h2 class="section-title">About Our Foundation</h2>
                    <p class="about-text">Marcesh Charty Foundation is dedicated to improving the lives of orphans and underprivileged children in Tanzania. We believe every child deserves access to education, basic necessities, and a hopeful future.</p>
                    <p class="about-text">Through school visits, donations of supplies, clothing, food, and emotional support, we work to create lasting positive change in the lives of vulnerable children.</p>
                    <a href="about.html" class="btn btn-primary">Learn More About Us</a>
                </div>
                <div class="col-lg-6">
                    <div class="about-image">
                        <div class="image-placeholder">
